title: AX PRO Break Caliper Spray Yellow Gloss 400ml
description: AX PRO Brake Caliper Spray Yellow Gloss 400ml Elevate the look of your vehicle's brake calipers with the AX PRO Brake Caliper Spray in vibrant yellow gloss. Designed to provide a durable and high-quality finish, this aerosol spray offers easy application and excellent coverage, giving your brake calipers a professional and eye-catching appearance. Key Features: Vibrant Yellow Gloss: Achieve a bold and attention-grabbing look for your brake calipers with the vibrant yellow gloss finish, adding a touch of style and personality to your vehicle. Durable Protection: Formulated to withstand high temperatures and resist brake dust, road debris, and other environmental elements, ensuring long-lasting protection and performance. Easy Application: The aerosol spray design allows for effortless and precise application, enabling you to achieve smooth and even coverage with minimal effort. Professional Finish: Provides a professional-quality finish that enhances the overall aesthetic of your vehicle, making your brake calipers stand out with a glossy and uniform appearance. Versatile Use: Suitable for use on both OEM and aftermarket brake calipers, as well as other automotive components, allowing you to customize and personalize your vehicle's look. Specifications: Product Type: Brake Caliper Spray Formulation: Aerosol Colour: Yellow Finish: Gloss Volume: 400ml Transform the look of your vehicle's brake calipers with the AX PRO Brake Caliper Spray in yellow gloss, delivering a vibrant and durable finish that enhances the visual appeal of your car or truck.
